1... d5
{ Again, this isn't winning any material, but Black activates his pieces and White's king will be in the middle for a long time. }
2. cxd5
{ 14.Qxd5  Qa5+  15.Ke2  Bg4+  16.f3  Rd8  -+  and   14.exd5  Bb4+  15.Ke2  Qh4  16.f3  e4  -+  are even worse. }
2... Bb4+
{ after   15.Ke2  Black will open the center with  15...O-O  followed by f5 and White's king won't survive for long.   14...Qa5+  -+  achieves basically the same. }
